C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=f10ef4dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/7nZoJVn.png</a>"},{"pid":"f3fc0dc05ea4c13818cbbdbd81a1fb65415dbe06","tid":1101310,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e83becb35ad7e4982261b088bcb41dfc43143c98","tid":1101310,"uid":142878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91ecafc8fe387fcefe5347d9bc29528dd89e3c32","tid":1101310,"uid":105446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d9ec1a414f0c8c8bdc45dbd09a41b22ba19d430","tid":1101310,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:01:53.000Z","msg":"個阿伯果然有料到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"阿伯咁勁都咁既田地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"遲下呢D只係基本功, 新世界人人都識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:23:04.000Z","msg":"以前講到精英海軍cp0先識之後部份海軍又識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebdfe1cfd1a92630cf9cbc023831f045d7b077b","tid":1101310,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b44efa9c968bd46c45862e8433aa6b3e987e33ac","tid":1101310,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:57:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/7nZoJVn.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nZoJVn.png&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUqC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=f10ef4dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/7nZoJVn.png</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"文字版<br />\n<br />\n第939話 老豹識途<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n索隆表明自己的身份，在日和得知索隆如果然如她所想是哥哥的伙伴後，十分安心。<br />\n<br />\n小南子是唯數不多的，知道日和身分的好友之一。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日和之所以沒有選擇跟他們一起穿越到未來，是為了以防萬一。<br />\n<br />\n假如沒能成功和桃之助他們會合，光月一族的血脈也不會就此斷掉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於索隆還不認識那些的伙伴：河松、傳次郎、阿修羅童子，就連日和也不知道如今他們身在何方，是否平安無事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路飛和豹大叔正在和犰狳SMILE果實能力者犰狳人戰鬥。<br />\n<br />\n路飛看起來總是在攻擊前停下並沒有直接攻擊他們，其實他是想像雷利和戰桃丸一樣，學會不接觸敵人就把人打飛的招式。<br />\n<br />\n他覺得只要領悟了這個招式，就一定能把凱多的鱗片打碎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n豹大叔感受到了路飛在尋求著某種東西，於是向他展示了路飛一直想領悟的招式，打倒了犰狳人。"},{"pid":"04348ccf0d1af668633b81ff7275a273b0bdab44","tid":1101310,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:35:04.000Z","msg":"依家霸氣都玩層次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出game又要"},{"pid":"fa9c5adfd97d584eb23c5753b33b97f2fe85c997","tid":1101310,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:05:04.000Z","msg":"好想快d睇"},{"pid":"d58459b69172db90842d68931a135037fd854878","tid":1101310,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fa9c5adfd97d584eb23c5753b33b97f2fe85c997","tid":1101310,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:05:04.000Z","msg":"好想快d睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"岩岩有封面好快有圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hgGiyfn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhgGiyfn.png&h=6b01e3e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1438c717c276570650f3041a421e8c232b8daad","tid":1101310,"uid":3020,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:42:44.000Z","msg":"直接抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20622ef672bf5f402ccf62e5c6e3675996389e18","tid":1101310,"uid":81919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a1438c717c276570650f3041a421e8c232b8daad","tid":1101310,"uid":3020,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:42:44.000Z","msg":"直接抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:48:43.000Z","msg":"俾我block左睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c42ab679a0512760de2067f8211eb63c8263be5","tid":1101310,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:25:31.000Z","msg":"但四王頭馬，卡二唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i